metadata.name: Fanningberg Runde
metadata.td:
Start at the church in Mariapfarr - towards Göriach - turn right onto a gravel road and continue to the barrier (KM 3.2) - uphill to KM 5.1, barrier - past the Pirka-Hof - downhill until you reach the main road, making a right - right at the next intersection - left at the intersection in Zankwarn, then immediately make a right - at the intersection next to a group of trees, turn right - after 100 m, make a right onto a gravel path (2x gates, trail M3) - on the paved road to Bruggarn - Fanning, making a right up the hill - at the Fanningberghof, turn left onto a forest road - Rader, paved road (KM 18.5) - downhill to St. Gertrauden - left - at the chapel, left to Steindorf - Seitling - right on the main road - left to Althofen - Mariapfarr.
Source: SLT / Alpintouren.at
